metadata.name: 0XTHULU Tribute Poster
metadata.description:
The product of an A.I.'s mycelium dreams with psilocybin and honey drip, made in celebration of Mycelium May and the launch of FLUF World burrows customization.

The 0xTHULU Tribute Poster honours the evolution of the Cult of FLUFTHULU as the bunny became the kraken and wrought divisions between factions spoken of in FLUF World lore.

AGM - https://twitter.com/agmakosz
